{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though he was Jewish and was-- in fact had been in a German concentration camp, the law was that aliens, any male aliens by definition had-- had to be in fact locked up.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was understandable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were in camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were not mistreated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were away from their activities, from their wives and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother also, because her nationality was German, had to leave Margate, which was considered to be a front line city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If there would have been an invasion, which was very much on the books in those days, they obviously would have landed in the south of England.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so all aliens had to be cleared out of this area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother had to live in London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there she joined the ARP, which was an air raid-- you know, the Air Raid Precautions organization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had a very fascinating experience on one occasion when a German pilot was shot down, came down by parachute and get himself entangled in the guttering of a house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the chief air raid warden was very concerned about the safety and told my mother, would you please tell him not to worry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're getting a ladder up and we're bringing a cup of tea up to him, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother said, you must be out of your mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That is a German swine up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, anyway, a long [LAUGHS] argument.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he gave my mother an order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Mendelsson, he said, this is an order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And having been brought up in Germany, an order was an order.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so she reluctantly obeyed the order and told this Nazi, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We're bringing up a cup of tea and we'll get you to safety.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is it?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So soon already.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
